[There is a correction of this report: Pertussis update (08): Americas, Europe, Australia, corr. 20190725.6586026
The report below stating that California is having a pertussis epidemic was published in 2014 when there actually was an epidemic. California is not currently experiencing a pertussis epidemic. ProMED-mail regrets the error. - Mod.ML]

