[Fontaine-les-Dijon, with a population of 9123 in 2016, is a commune in the Dijon arrondissement, Cote-d'Or department, Bourgogne-Franche-Comte region in eastern France, 317 km (197 miles) southeast of Paris (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fontaine-les-Dijon). A map showing the location of Fontaine-les-Dijon can be found at https://www.google.com/maps/place/21121+Fontaine-lès-Dijon,+France. - Mod.ML

